metadata.name: Free Simon Tadros
metadata.description: This is Simon Tadros, Lebanese tech entrepreneur and crypto enthusiast. I am targeted in a cryptocurrency related legal set up by malicious actors that resulted in my arrest using false witness and accusations. I remain detained in Belgium due to prosecutor incompetence and inability to make sound judgment.To provide legal support seek more information about my case please contact me personally on twitter @spuriousdragon.I am also accepting donations to sustain my legal battle on this Ethereum address: 0xE4cFcb0e2053618Cd2720aDA3562cE5FE38aCe85
